프로젝트 `D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest`에서 작업합니다. Next.js App Router 구조입니다. 다음이 이미 커밋돼 있습니다:
- `lib/site-types.ts`
- `lib/site-manager.ts`
- `lib/url-normalizer.ts`

기존 API 패턴은 `app/api/scenarios/route.ts`와 `app/api/scenarios/[id]/route.ts`를 참고하세요.

**목표:** 두 API 라우트 파일을 생성하고 커밋합니다.

**규칙:** 아래 두 파일만 생성하세요. 다른 파일 절대 수정 금지.

---

**`app/api/sites/route.ts` 생성** (디렉터리도 함께 생성):

```ts
import { NextResponse } from "next/server";
import type { NextRequest } from "next/server";
import { listSites, saveSite } from "@/lib/site-manager";
import { isHttpUrl } from "@/lib/url-normalizer";
import type { Site } from "@/lib/site-types";

export async function GET() {
  return NextResponse.json({ success: true, data: listSites() });
}

export async function POST(req: NextRequest) {
  try {
    const body = (await req.json()) as Site;
    validate(body);
    const now = new Date().toISOString();
    saveSite({ ...body, createdAt: now, updatedAt: now });
    return NextResponse.json({ success: true, data: body });
  } catch (error) {
    return NextResponse.json(
      { success: false, error: error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error) },
      { status: 400 }
    );
  }
}

function validate(site: Site) {
  if (!site.id || !/^[\w-]+$/.test(site.id)) throw new Error("Invalid id");
  if (!site.name?.trim()) throw new Error("name required");
  if (!Array.isArray(site.crawl?.startUrls) || site.crawl.startUrls.length === 0) {
    throw new Error("startUrls required");
  }
  for (const u of site.crawl.startUrls) {
    if (!isHttpUrl(u)) throw new Error(`startUrl not http(s): ${u}`);
  }
  for (const pat of [...(site.crawl.includePatterns ?? []), ...(site.crawl.excludePatterns ?? [])]) {
    try { new RegExp(pat); } catch { throw new Error(`Bad regex: ${pat}`); }
  }
}
```

**`app/api/sites/[id]/route.ts` 생성** (디렉터리도 함께 생성):

```ts
import { NextResponse } from "next/server";
import type { NextRequest } from "next/server";
import { deleteSite, getSite, saveSite } from "@/lib/site-manager";

export async function GET(_: NextRequest, { params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  const site = getSite(params.id);
  if (!site) return NextResponse.json({ success: false, error: "Not found" }, { status: 404 });
  return NextResponse.json({ success: true, data: site });
}

export async function PUT(req: NextRequest, { params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  const existing = getSite(params.id);
  if (!existing) return NextResponse.json({ success: false, error: "Not found" }, { status: 404 });
  const patch = await req.json();
  const merged = { ...existing, ...patch, id: existing.id, updatedAt: new Date().toISOString() };
  saveSite(merged);
  return NextResponse.json({ success: true, data: merged });
}

export async function DELETE(_: NextRequest, { params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  return NextResponse.json({ success: deleteSite(params.id) });
}
```

**tsc 확인:**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && npx tsc --noEmit 2>&1 | head -20
```

**커밋:**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && git add app/api/sites/route.ts "app/api/sites/[id]/route.ts" && git commit -m "feat(site): add Site CRUD API routes"
```

결과를 한 줄로 보고: "tsc clean, committed" 또는 실패 내용.

